Used for business truth
Stores users, resellers, dealers, devices, keys, EMI, payments, lock requests, commands, audit/security, location, fraud/evidence indexes" style="shape=cylinder3d;boundedLbl=1;backgroundOutline=1;size=15;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fce7f3;strokeColor=#db2777;fontColor=#500724;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="150" width="507" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="ne4f316706521" value="Redis / Upstash
Used for volatile state
Refresh token hashes, blacklist, temp tokens, device OTP, rate limits, command nonces, Bull queue state" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ede9fe;strokeColor=#7c3aed;fontColor=#2e1065;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="611" y="150" width="507" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="na83d1e016654" value="Firebase / FCM
Used for push transport
Sends lock/unlock/message/location commands
Stores/uses FCM tokens; not the business source of truth" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ede9fe;strokeColor=#7c3aed;fontColor=#2e1065;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1142" y="150" width="507" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="na56ce26ad11b" value="Google AMAPI / Android Enterprise
Used/planned for DPC provisioning, policy, managed account, FRP release
Stores enterprise device/account state inside Google systems" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ede9fe;strokeColor=#7c3aed;fontColor=#2e1065;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1673" y="150" width="507" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="nf6ede1611a44" value="Google Drive
Used by Flutter dealer/reseller optional vault backup
Encrypted vault snapshot only if user binds account
Developer should review retention and encryption keys" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ede9fe;strokeColor=#7c3aed;fontColor=#2e1065;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="490" width="507" height="260" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n430d51e0ead7" value="Email/SMS providers
