Full backend authority
Approve resellers/key requests
Device actions
Decoupling execution
Security/NEIR/audit oversight
Risk: highest blast radius" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fee2e2;strokeColor=#dc2626;fontColor=#450a0a;fontStyle=1;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="80" y="150" width="507" height="290" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n3c02ff135756" value="Reseller
Business authority over dealers/stock
Can request keys and assign keys
Can create/manage dealers
Cannot directly lock phones
Cannot decouple device" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontColor=#052e16;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="611" y="150" width="507" height="290" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n7ecd0eaffca7" value="Dealer
Operational authority at point of sale
Enrolls devices
Manages EMI/customer interaction
Can submit lock/location/message/unlock requests
Server verifies before enforcement" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#dcfce7;strokeColor=#16a34a;fontColor=#052e16;fontSize=12;spacing=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1142" y="150" width="507" height="290" as="geometry"/></mxCell><mxCell id="n520c1ed74f88" value="Customer/User app
Phone-side enforcement authority only after Device Owner
Cannot decide business status
